---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Hizmet Bölgesi"
  description="Yiğiter Orman Ürünleri — Türkiye hizmet ağı. Depo lokasyonları, sevkiyat alanları, bölgesel bayiler."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-12 lg:py-16 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-accent font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Operasyon</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 leading-tight">
          Türkiye Geneli Hizmet
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">
          İstanbul ve Tosya'daki depolarımız ve bayilerimiz üzerinden Türkiye'nin her yerine hizmet veriyoruz.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">

        <!-- Sol: Harita -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Depo & Bayı Lokasyonları</h2>

          <!-- Google My Maps Embed -->
          <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-200 mb-6" style="height: 420px;">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=1EeHCH3JvvfbKZnkSh_jbVsem3NgLf-s"
              width="100%"
              height="100%"
              style="border:0;"
              allowfullscreen=""
              loading="lazy"
              referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
              title="Yiğiter Orman Ürünleri — Depo Lokasyonları"
            ></iframe>
          </div>

          <!-- Türkiye Geneli Not -->
          <div class="bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-5 flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7 12a5 5 0 1110 0A5 5 0 017 12z" />
            </svg>
            <div>
              <p class="text-primary font-semibold text-sm">Türkiye Geneline Sevkiyat</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs mt-1">
                Kastamonu Entegre ürünlerinde Türkiye'nin her yerine sevkiyat imkanı sunuyoruz. Depolarımızdan 48-72 saat içerisinde teslimat gerçekleşir.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sağ: Depo Bilgileri -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Operasyon Merkezleri</h2>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <!-- Şube 1: Kapı Ürünleri / Başakşehir 24. Blok -->
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 hover:border-primary/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">Kapı Ürünleri — Başakşehir</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">İstanbul, Avrupa Yakası</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Stoklu Ürünler:</strong> Kapı kasası, pervaz, melamin kapı yüzeyleri, kapı imalat malzemeleri (kağıt dolgu, PVC film)
              </p>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded p-3 text-xs text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                <p class="font-medium">İkitelli Keresteciler Sitesi, Ziyagökalp Mah., 23. Sokak, 24. Blok No:38/40</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500">Başakşehir / İstanbul</p>
                <div class="flex gap-3 pt-1">
                  <a href="tel:+902126702025" class="text-accent font-medium hover:underline">0212 670 2025</a>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
                  <a href="tel:+905415157667" class="text-accent font-medium hover:underline">0541 515 7667</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Şube 2: Boya Avrupa Yakası / Başakşehir 18. Blok -->
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 hover:border-primary/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">Boya Satış — Başakşehir (Avrupa Yakası)</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">İstanbul, Avrupa Yakası</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Stoklu Ürünler:</strong> Genç Boya ürünleri (boya, vernik, astar, sertleştirici, tiner) — Genç Boya Avrupa Yakası Bayi
              </p>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded p-3 text-xs text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                <p class="font-medium">İkitelli Keresteciler Sitesi, Ziyagökalp Mah., 18. Blok No:19/21</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500">Başakşehir / İstanbul</p>
                <div class="flex gap-3 pt-1">
                  <a href="tel:+902126700038" class="text-accent font-medium hover:underline">0212 670 0038</a>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
                  <a href="tel:+905417602735" class="text-accent font-medium hover:underline">0541 760 2735</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Şube 3: MDF/Panel Satış / Başakşehir Deparko -->
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 hover:border-primary/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">MDF & Panel Satış — Deparko</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">İstanbul, Avrupa Yakası</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Stoklu Ürünler:</strong> Kastamonu Entegre ürünleri (yongalevha/sunta, MDF, MDFLam, paneller) — Ana Bayi
              </p>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded p-3 text-xs text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                <p class="font-medium">Hürriyet Bulvarı, Deparko Sanayi Sitesi, 785/5 No:1</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500">Başakşehir / İstanbul</p>
                <div class="pt-1">
                  <a href="tel:+905464886737" class="text-accent font-medium hover:underline">0546 488 6737</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Şube 6: Boya Anadolu Yakası / Ümraniye -->
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 hover:border-primary/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">Boya Satış — Ümraniye (Anadolu Yakası)</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">İstanbul, Anadolu Yakası</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Stoklu Ürünler:</strong> Genç Boya ürünleri — Genç Boya Anadolu Yakası Distribütörü
              </p>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded p-3 text-xs text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                <p class="font-medium">Necip Fazıl Bulvarı, Keyap Sanayi Sitesi No:44/133 H Blok</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500">Ümraniye / İstanbul</p>
                <div class="pt-1">
                  <a href="tel:+905333876756" class="text-accent font-medium hover:underline">0533 387 6756</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Şube 4: Merkez Satış / Tosya -->
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 hover:border-primary/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">Merkez Satış — Tosya</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Kastamonu, Tosya (Karadeniz Bölgesi)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Stoklu Ürünler:</strong> Genç Boya Tosya Bayisi — Karadeniz bölgesi hizmet merkezi
              </p>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded p-3 text-xs text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                <p class="font-medium">Harsat Mahallesi, 8. Yukarı Sanayi Sokak No:5</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500">Tosya / Kastamonu</p>
                <div class="flex gap-3 pt-1">
                  <a href="tel:+903663137667" class="text-accent font-medium hover:underline">0366 313 7667</a>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
                  <a href="tel:+905417177667" class="text-accent font-medium hover:underline">0541 717 7667</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Şube 5: Üretim Tesisi / Tosya Kurtbeli OSB -->
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 hover:border-accent/40 hover:shadow-sm transition-all ring-1 ring-accent/20">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-3">
                <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">Üretim Tesisi — Tosya Kurtbeli OSB</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Kastamonu, Tosya — Kendi Üretimimiz</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-3">
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Üretilen Ürünler:</strong> Kapı kasası (standart & özel ölçü), kapı pervazı — seri üretim ve proje bazlı
              </p>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded p-3 text-xs text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                <p class="font-medium">Karasapaca Köyü, Kurtbeli OSB Mevkii, 3. Cadde No:2, İç Kapı:1</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500">Tosya / Kastamonu</p>
                <div class="pt-1">
                  <a href="tel:+905418187667" class="text-accent font-medium hover:underline">0541 818 7667</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- CTA -->
          <div class="mt-8 p-5 bg-accent/10 border border-accent/30 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-accent text-sm mb-2">Bölgenize Ait Depo İletişim</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs mb-3">
              Konumunuza ait depo ile doğrudan iletişim kurmak için aşağıdaki butona tıklayabilirsiniz.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/iletisim"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-dark text-white font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm transition-colors"
            >
              İletişime Geç
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Teslimat Politikası -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-12 lg:py-16 border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-8 text-center">Sevkiyat & Teslimat</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 text-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm mb-2">Hızlı Sevkiyat</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Depolarımızdan 48-72 saat içerisinde sevkiyat</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 text-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM19 17a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16V6a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a1 1 0 00-1 1v10a1 1 0 001 1h1m8-1a1 1 0 01-1 1H9m4-1V8a1 1 0 011-1h2.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l3.414 3.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V16a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1m-6-1a1 1 0 001 1h1M5 17a2 2 0 104 0m-4 0a2 2 0 114 0m6 0a2 2 0 104 0m-4 0a2 2 0 114 0" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm mb-2">Türkiye Geneli</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Tüm Türkiye'ye sevkiyat hizmetleri</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 text-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.354 15.354A9 9 0 015.646 5.646 9.001 9.001 0 0020.354 15.354z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm mb-2">Stok Kontrol</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Geniş stok yelpazemizle anında hazır</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 text-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm mb-2">Destek</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Sevkiyat ve ürün desteği</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
